Text: Mine was "precracked" but I'll, upload my preference file for you.

So, this worked like a charm, right "out of the box".

It asked for a registration key the first time it was opened, by you can put - literally - any number in there, and it works.

Personally, I used "1234" and hit the 'register' button.  All is well, and the app says "Registered to: ." at the bottom of the main window.

I dunno why it says it's registered to a period, but it works just fine and doesn't ask for a key, or complain in any way.

Thanks!
